Seahawks @ 49ers on 10/22 #TNF WUSA 1:11 p.m. EDT October 22, 2015 Thursday Night Football. CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
WASHINGTON (WUSA9) -- #TNF on WUSA9! 
Division rivalry as The Seahawks @ 49ers take the field. Both teams are 2-4 and need a win! Seattle is in third place in the NFC West and San Francisco is behind them. 
Game will kick-off at approximately 8:26 p.m. on October 22. 
Will The Seahawks overcome their fourth quarter collapse? 
49ers are looking for back-to-back wins. Strong play against The Ravens last week. 
Who will claim victory tonight? Tune in to find out! 
For coverage leading up to the game, watch WUSA9 News at 5 p.m., 6 p.m. and 7 p.m. 
NFL Thursday Night Kick-off Pre-Game Show airs at 7:30 p.m. 
After the game, WUSA9 News is scheduled at 11:15 p.m. and The Late Show With Stephen Colbert at 11:50 p.m. Times will slide if football overrun. 
Football starts here!
